in its purest form.

00:00:57.850 --> 00:01:00.329
MATIAS CASTELLO: Design is a
big, big part of what we do.

00:01:00.329 --> 00:01:01.870
And the photos are
not created by us.

00:01:01.870 --> 00:01:04.340
So what we try to
build and design

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:07.500
is a canvas for any photo
to look at its best.

00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:09.850
We made several changes
to make our app simpler,

00:01:09.850 --> 00:01:11.200
to streamline the experience.

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:16.080
And that definitely plays
into our engagement metrics.

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:18.180
The most visible one
is probably the menu.

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:21.170
We removed several items
from the navigation

00:01:21.170 --> 00:01:23.129
to make it clearer
what EyeEm is about.

00:01:23.129 --> 00:01:25.670
Now you have access to the three
main parts of the app, which

00:01:25.670 --> 00:01:28.200
