which is where you find

00:01:32.690 --> 00:01:35.023
all the photos of your friends
and the photographers you

00:01:35.023 --> 00:01:37.860
follow; and Missions are photo
competitions where people post

00:01:37.860 --> 00:01:40.880
photos around a certain topic,
and then win prizes, and get

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:42.250
published.

00:01:42.250 --> 00:01:46.560
